					"type": 23,
					"value": "1. DebugBook > Goto Region: Act 2 > ShadowCurseLands > Mountain Pass Entry. \r\n\r\n2. Goto 57.566; 42.958; 134.421\r\n3. Agree to help fight the shadow creatures\r\n4. reCon killCombat\r\n5. Agree to follow them to Haven\r\n6. At CheckPoint Cinematic, press choice 1 all the way.\r\n7. Follow Harper Karrow all the way to a small makeshift altar\r\n8. Talk to her to trigger dialogue"
